tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE quantum_communication_data (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    sender VARCHAR(255),
    receiver VARCHAR(255),
    message TEXT,
    communication_time TIMESTAMP,
    quantum_state VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE quantum_communications (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    sender VARCHAR(50),
    receiver VARCHAR(50),
    message TEXT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE data_mining_analysis (
    analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    dataset_id INT,
    analysis_date DATE,
    analysis_results TEXT,
    FOREIGN KEY (dataset_id) REFERENCES quantum_communication_datasets(dataset_id)
);

CREATE TABLE insights_extracted (
    insight_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    analysis_id INT,
    insight_text TEXT,
    insight_date DATE,
    FOREIGN KEY (analysis_id) REFERENCES data_mining_analysis(analysis_id)
);

CREATE TABLE communication_metadata (
    communication_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    dataset_id INT,
    sender_name TEXT,
    receiver_name TEXT,
    communication_date TIMESTAMP
);
